data.description:
Welcome to 280 E Putnam Ave, Porterville, CA 93257 - a charming two-story family home with a covered patio entrance that invites you into a world of comfort and elegance. This cozy residence features a landscaped front yard, a dedicated home office, and a spacious master bedroom with a large walk-in closet.

As you enter through the covered patio, the warm and welcoming atmosphere sets the tone for a truly inviting home. The thoughtful layout provides a perfect balance of functionality and style, making it an ideal space for family living.

Discover the convenience of a well-appointed kitchen, modern amenities, and the unique charm of this family-friendly home. Don't miss the opportunity to make 280 E Putnam Ave your own. Schedule your viewing today and step into a haven where comfort and style come together effortlessly!
